Text:
For those who have the instructions unclear:

Install, run, register account here, enable the GPS when it asks you too,don't activate the traffic thing afterwards(unless you need it), DL your maps and you're good to go.

Just tested in Budapest, Hungary and Vienna, Austria on Motorola Defy.  I had earlier iGo, Sygic, Navignon, TomTom, but none of them were doing the job like this one. So far the best navigation system on Android. Thank's for the upload ScorpioPirate.

Thanks guy's.... I have lots of uploads, and lots of seeders, but not many that comment my uploads :)

Happy new year to all :)
